data.description: Delightful, corner lot, single story home nicely set on .58 acres. This enticing one level home offers step-savings days and uncluttered living with 3 bedrooms, and 2 baths. Look into the additional conveniences, such as 2 wood burning fireplaces, newer flooring, kitchen appliances included, and large two- car garage. Covered porch at the entrance and large open fenced in yard out back. You won't find many places that say 'home' as eloquently as this one!
